                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">McCreery</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Tegucigalpa</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-10-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 3, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. McCreery states that Madriz left Amapala for Mexico via La Union, this date,
                    a.m.</p>
            </div>
